{"title_page": "Elvin Yunuszade", "text_new": "{{short description|Azerbaijani footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2011}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name        = Elvin Yunuszade\n| image       = Elvin Yunuszade.jpg\n| image_size  = 200\n| caption     = \n| fullname    = Elvin Garib oglu Yunuszade\n| birth_date  = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1992|08|22}}\n| birth_place = [[Qazax|Qazakh]], [[Azerbaijan]]\n| height      = 1.91 m\n| currentclub = [[NK \u010celik Zenica|\u010celik Zenica]]\n| clubnumber  = 22\n| position    = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n| youthyears1 = \n| youthclubs1 = \n| years1 = 2010\u20132015   | clubs1 = [[Neftchi Baku PFK|Neftchi Baku]]    | caps1 = 75   | goals1 = 1\n| years2 = 2010\u20132011   | clubs2 = \u2192 [[Simurq PFC|Simurq]]  (loan)      | caps2 = 31   | goals2 = 2\n| years3 = 2015\u20132018   | clubs3 = [[Qaraba\u011f FK|Qaraba\u011f]]               | caps3 = 52   | goals3 = 3\n| years4 = 2018\u20132019   | clubs4 = [[Sabah FK|Sabah]]                   | caps4 = 2    | goals4 = 0\n| years5 = 2019        | clubs5 = [[Sabail FK|Sabail]]                 | caps5 = 23   | goals5 = 2\n| years6 = 2020\u2013       | clubs6 = [[NK \u010celik Zenica|\u010celik Zenica]]     | caps6 = 0    | goals6 = 0\n| nationalyears1 = 2012\u20132013  | nationalteam1 = [[Azerbaijan national under-21 football team|Azerbaijan U21]] | nationalcaps1 = 3  | nationalgoals1 = 0\n| nationalyears2 = 2014\u2013      | nationalteam2 = [[Azerbaijan national football team|Azerbaijan]]              | nationalcaps2 = 3  | nationalgoals2 = 1\n| pcupdate = 20 February 2020\n| ntupdate = 5 March 2014\n}}\n\n''' Elvin Yunuszade''' ({{lang-az|Elvin Yunuszad\u0259}}; born 22 August 1992 in [[Qazax|Qazakh]]) is an [[Azerbaijani people|Azerbaijani]] [[football (soccer)|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|centre back]] for [[NK \u010celik Zenica|\u010celik Zenica]] in the [[Premier League of Bosnia and Herzegovina]].\n\n==Career==\n===Club===\nOn 24 May 2018, [[Qaraba\u011f FK]] announced that Yunuszade had been released by the club following expiration of his contract.<ref>{{cite web|title=Qaraba\u011f FK-dan bildiri\u015f|url=http://www.qarabagh.com/index.php?name=newsread&type=3&news_id=11244&lang=1|website=qarabagh.com/|publisher=Qaraba\u011f FK|accessdate=24 May 2018|language=Azerbaijani|date=24 May 2018}}</ref>\n\nOn 9 January 2019, [[Sabail FK|Sabail]] announced the singing of Yunuszade.<ref>{{cite web|title=Meet our new central defender! Elvin Yunuszade!|url=https://www.facebook.com/SabailFC/photos/pb.1732087423706184.-2207520000.1547062282./2244739595774295/?type=3&theater|website=facebook.com|publisher=Sabail FK|accessdate=9 January 2019|language=English|date=9 January 2019}}</ref> On 21 December 2019, Yunuszade left Sabail by mutual consent.<ref>{{cite web|title=ELVIN YUNUSZAD\u018fNIN M\u00dcQAVIL\u018fSIN\u018f XITAM VERILIB|url=https://sabailfc.az/az/2019/12/21/elvin-yunuszad\u0259nin-muqavil\u0259sin\u0259-xitam-verilib/|website=sabailfc.az|publisher=FK Sabail|accessdate=25 December 2019 |date=21 December 2019 |language=Azerbaijani}}</ref>\n\nOn 9 February 2020, Yunuszade signed contract with [[NK \u010celik Zenica]] until the end of the 2019\u201320 season.<ref>{{cite web|title=Elvin Yunuszad\u0259 \u201c\u00c7elik\u201dl\u0259 m\u00fcqavil\u0259 ba\u011flad\u0131|url=https://www.sportinfo.az/idman_xeberleri/sabah/77942.html|website=sportinfo.az|publisher=Sportinfo|date=13 February 2020 |language=Azerbaijani}}</ref>\n\n===International===\nYunuszade made his debut for the [[Azerbaijan national football team|senior national team of his country]] on 5 March 2014, scoring the winning goal in the 1:0 victory over [[Philippines national football team|Philippines]] in a [[friendly match]].<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.flashscore.com/match/n7LjTK0U/#match-summary|title=Azerbaijan vs. Philippines 1:0|accessdate=2014-03-07 |date=2014-03-05 |publisher=flashscore.com}}</ref>\n\n==Career statistics==\n===Club===\n{{updated|match played 1 December 2018}}<ref>{{Soccerway|elvin-yunuszade/211199|Elvin Yunuszad\u0259}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|+ Appearances and goals by club, season and competition\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!colspan=\"3\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|National Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|Continental\n!colspan=\"2\"|Other\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Division!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\" |[[Neft\u00e7i PFK|Neftchi Baku]]\n|[[2010\u201311 Neftchi Baku PFC season|2010\u201311]]\n|rowspan=\"5\" |[[Azerbaijan Premier League|Premier League]]\n|0||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||0||0\n|-\n|[[2011\u201312 Neftchi Baku PFC season|2011\u201312]]\n|10||0||3||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||13||0\n|-\n|[[2012\u201313 Neftchi Baku PFC season|2012\u201313]]\n|24||0||5||2||9||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||38||2\n|-\n|[[2013\u201314 Neftchi Baku PFC season|2013\u201314]]\n|20||1||6||0||1||0||0||0||27||1\n|-\n|[[2014\u201315 Neftchi Baku PFC season|2014\u201315]]\n|21||0||4||0||6||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||31||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!75!!1!!18!!2!!16!!0!!0!!0!!109!!3\n|-\n|[[Simurq PIK|Simurq]] (loan)\n|[[2010\u201311 Simurq PFC season|2010\u201311]]\n|[[Azerbaijan Premier League|Premier League]]\n|31||2||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||32||2\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\" valign=\"center\"|[[FK Qaraba\u011f|Qaraba\u011f]]\n|[[2015\u201316 FK Qaraba\u011f season|2015\u201316]]\n|rowspan=\"3\" valign=\"center\"|[[Azerbaijan Premier League|Premier League]]\n|19||0||4||0||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||25||0\n|-\n|[[2016\u201317 FK Qaraba\u011f season|2016\u201317]]\n|13||1||4||0||4||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||21||1\n|-\n|[[2017\u201318 FK Qaraba\u011f season|2017\u201318]]\n|20||2||3||0||5||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||28||2\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!52!!3!!11!!0!!11!!0!!-!!-!!74!!3\n|-\n|[[Sabah FK|Sabah]]\n|[[2018\u201319 Sabah FK season|2018\u201319]]\n|[[Azerbaijan Premier League|Premier League]]\n|2||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||2||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total\n!160!!6!!30!!2!!27!!0!!0!!0!!217!!8\n|}\n\n===International===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!colspan=3|[[Azerbaijan national football team|Azerbaijan]]\n|-\n!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|2014||3||1\n|-\n!Total||3||1\n|}\n''Statistics accurate as of match played 16 November 2014''<ref name=\"NFT Stats\">{{NFT player|id=54786|name=Elvin Yunuszad\u0259|accessdate=24 May 2018}}</ref>\n\n===International goal===\n:''Scores and results list Azerbaijan's goal tally first.''\n{| class=\"wikitable\" border=\"1\"\n|-\n! # !! Date !! Venue !! Opponent !! Score !! Result !! Competition\n|-\n| 1. || 5 March 2014 || [[Maktoum Bin Rashid Al Maktoum Stadium]], [[Dubai]], [[United Arab Emirates]] || {{fb|Philippines}} || '''1'''\u20130 || 1\u20130 || [[Exhibition game|Friendly match]]\n|-\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n;Neftchi Baku\n*[[Azerbaijan Premier League]] (2): [[2011\u201312 Azerbaijan Premier League|2011\u201312]], [[2012\u201313 Azerbaijan Premier League|2012\u201313]]\n*[[Azerbaijan Cup]] (1): [[2012\u201313 Azerbaijan Cup|2012\u201313]]\n\n;Qaraba\u011f\n*[[Azerbaijan Premier League]] (3): [[2015\u201316 Azerbaijan Premier League|2015\u201316]], [[2016\u201317 Azerbaijan Premier League|2016\u201317]], [[2017\u201318 Azerbaijan Premier League|2017\u201318]]\n*[[Azerbaijan Cup]]: (1) [[2015\u201316 Azerbaijan Cup|2015-16]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://www.nkcelik.ba/igraci/ nkcelik.ba]\n* {{FootballDatabase.eu|167900}}\n* {{Soccerway|elvin-yunuszade/211199}}\n\n{{NK \u010celik Zenica squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Yunuszade, Elvin}}\n[[Category:1992 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Qazakh]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:Azerbaijani footballers]]\n[[Category:Azerbaijani expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Azerbaijan Premier League players]]\n[[Category:Premier League of Bosnia and Herzegovina players]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Bosnia and Herzegovina]]\n[[Category:Simurq PIK players]]\n[[Category:Qaraba\u011f FK players]]\n[[Category:Neft\u00e7i PFK players]]\n[[Category:Sabah FC players]]\n[[Category:Sabail FK players]]\n[[Category:NK \u010celik Zenica players]]\n\n{{Azerbaijan-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2011}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name        = Elvin Yunuszade\n| image       = Elvin Yunuszade.jpg\n| image_size  = 200\n| caption     = \n| fullname    = Elvin Garib oglu Yunuszade\n| birth_date  = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1992|08|22}}\n| birth_place = [[Qazax|Qazakh]], [[Azerbaijan]]\n| height      = 1.91 m\n| currentclub = [[NK \u010celik Zenica|\u010celik Zenica]]\n| clubnumber  = 22\n| position    = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n| youthyears1 = \n| youthclubs1 = \n| years1 = 2010\u20132015   | clubs1 = [[Neftchi Baku PFK|Neftchi Baku]]    | caps1 = 75   | goals1 = 1\n| years2 = 2010\u20132011   | clubs2 = \u2192 [[Simurq PFC|Simurq]]  (loan)      | caps2 = 31   | goals2 = 2\n| years3 = 2015\u20132018   | clubs3 = [[Qaraba\u011f FK|Qaraba\u011f]]               | caps3 = 52   | goals3 = 3\n| years4 = 2018\u20132019   | clubs4 = [[Sabah FK|Sabah]]                   | caps4 = 2    | goals4 = 0\n| years5 = 2019        | clubs5 = [[Sabail FK|Sabail]]                 | caps5 = 23   | goals5 = 2\n| years6 = 2020\u2013       | clubs6 = [[NK \u010celik Zenica|\u010celik Zenica]]     | caps6 = 0    | goals6 = 0\n| nationalyears1 = 2012\u20132013  | nationalteam1 = [[Azerbaijan national under-21 football team|Azerbaijan U21]] | nationalcaps1 = 3  | nationalgoals1 = 0\n| nationalyears2 = 2014\u2013      | nationalteam2 = [[Azerbaijan national football team|Azerbaijan]]              | nationalcaps2 = 3  | nationalgoals2 = 1\n| pcupdate = 20 February 2020\n| ntupdate = 5 March 2014\n}}\n\n''' Elvin Yunuszade''' ({{lang-az|Elvin Yunuszad\u0259}}; born 22 August 1992 in [[Qazax|Qazakh]]) is an [[Azerbaijani people|Azerbaijani]] [[football (soccer)|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|centre back]] for [[NK \u010celik Zenica|\u010celik Zenica]] in the [[Premier League of Bosnia and Herzegovina]].\n\n==Career==\n===Club===\nOn 24 May 2018, [[Qaraba\u011f FK]] announced that Yunuszade had been released by the club following expiration of his contract.<ref>{{cite web|title=Qaraba\u011f FK-dan bildiri\u015f|url=http://www.qarabagh.com/index.php?name=newsread&type=3&news_id=11244&lang=1|website=qarabagh.com/|publisher=Qaraba\u011f FK|accessdate=24 May 2018|language=Azerbaijani|date=24 May 2018}}</ref>\n\nOn 9 January 2019, [[Sabail FK|Sabail]] announced the singing of Yunuszade.<ref>{{cite web|title=Meet our new central defender! Elvin Yunuszade!|url=https://www.facebook.com/SabailFC/photos/pb.1732087423706184.-2207520000.1547062282./2244739595774295/?type=3&theater|website=facebook.com|publisher=Sabail FK|accessdate=9 January 2019|language=English|date=9 January 2019}}</ref> On 21 December 2019, Yunuszade left Sabail by mutual consent.<ref>{{cite web|title=ELVIN YUNUSZAD\u018fNIN M\u00dcQAVIL\u018fSIN\u018f XITAM VERILIB|url=https://sabailfc.az/az/2019/12/21/elvin-yunuszad\u0259nin-muqavil\u0259sin\u0259-xitam-verilib/|website=sabailfc.az|publisher=FK Sabail|accessdate=25 December 2019 |date=21 December 2019 |language=Azerbaijani}}</ref>\n\nOn 9 February 2020, Yunuszade signed contract with [[NK \u010celik Zenica]] until the end of the 2019\u201320 season.<ref>{{cite web|title=Elvin Yunuszad\u0259 \u201c\u00c7elik\u201dl\u0259 m\u00fcqavil\u0259 ba\u011flad\u0131|url=https://www.sportinfo.az/idman_xeberleri/sabah/77942.html|website=sportinfo.az|publisher=Sportinfo|date=13 February 2020 |language=Azerbaijani}}</ref>\n\n===International===\nYunuszade made his debut for the [[Azerbaijan national football team|senior national team of his country]] on 5 March 2014, scoring the winning goal in the 1:0 victory over [[Philippines national football team|Philippines]] in a [[friendly match]].<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.flashscore.com/match/n7LjTK0U/#match-summary|title=Azerbaijan vs. Philippines 1:0|accessdate=2014-03-07 |date=2014-03-05 |publisher=flashscore.com}}</ref>\n\n==Career statistics==\n===Club===\n{{updated|match played 1 December 2018}}<ref>{{Soccerway|elvin-yunuszade/211199|Elvin Yunuszad\u0259}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|+ Appearances and goals by club, season and competition\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!colspan=\"3\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|National Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|Continental\n!colspan=\"2\"|Other\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Division!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\" |[[Neft\u00e7i PFK|Neftchi Baku]]\n|[[2010\u201311 Neftchi Baku PFC season|2010\u201311]]\n|rowspan=\"5\" |[[Azerbaijan Premier League|Premier League]]\n|0||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||0||0\n|-\n|[[2011\u201312 Neftchi Baku PFC season|2011\u201312]]\n|10||0||3||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||13||0\n|-\n|[[2012\u201313 Neftchi Baku PFC season|2012\u201313]]\n|24||0||5||2||9||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||38||2\n|-\n|[[2013\u201314 Neftchi Baku PFC season|2013\u201314]]\n|20||1||6||0||1||0||0||0||27||1\n|-\n|[[2014\u201315 Neftchi Baku PFC season|2014\u201315]]\n|21||0||4||0||6||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||31||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!75!!1!!18!!2!!16!!0!!0!!0!!109!!3\n|-\n|[[Simurq PIK|Simurq]] (loan)\n|[[2010\u201311 Simurq PFC season|2010\u201311]]\n|[[Azerbaijan Premier League|Premier League]]\n|31||2||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||32||2\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\" valign=\"center\"|[[FK Qaraba\u011f|Qaraba\u011f]]\n|[[2015\u201316 FK Qaraba\u011f season|2015\u201316]]\n|rowspan=\"3\" valign=\"center\"|[[Azerbaijan Premier League|Premier League]]\n|19||0||4||0||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||25||0\n|-\n|